  +files/xerces-c-2.7.0-multilib.patch, xerces-c-2.6.0-r1.ebuild,
  xerces-c-2.7.0.ebuild:
  Make 2.6.0-r1 and 2.7.0 multilib safe, and mark 2.6.0-r1 stable.  Bug #106228

